    " -----------------------------------------------------------
        nmap * *Nzz
        nmap # #Nzz
    " }}}
    " Disable Arrows {{{2
    " --------------
        nmap <Left> :vertical resize -5<CR>
        nmap <Up> :resize -5<CR>
        nmap <Right> :vertical resize +5<CR>
        nmap <Down> :resize +5<CR>
        imap <Left> <Esc><Esc>a
        imap <Up> <Esc><Esc>a
        imap <Right> <Esc><Esc>a
        imap <Down> <Esc><Esc>a
    " }}}
    " Y y$ Fix {{{2
    " --------
        " Why the hell isn't this the normal behavior?
        nnoremap Y y$
    " }}}
    " Easy Window Switching {{{2
    " ---------------------
        map <C-h> <C-w>h
        map <C-j> <C-w>j
        map <C-k> <C-w>k
        map <C-l> <C-w>l
    " }}}
    " Space folds and unfolds {{{2
    " -----------------------
        nnoremap <Space> za
        vnoremap <Space> za
    " }}}
